data.description: TURNKEY Renovated Unit in Desirable Honolulu LOCATION steps away from Shopping, Dining & Ala Moana! Enjoy 2 Split AC's fully approved for the Unit & Maintenance Fee Includes Electricity! Kitchen is Open to the Dining Area & a Spacious Living Room has great Natural Light with a huge Lanai boasting the Pool View! Secure Parking Garage, Fob-Entry Lobby, Lounge & Laundry Area. Hawai’i Honolulu Lifestyle near to Ala Moana Shopping Center & Beach Park will make live, work and play an enjoyable way to be the New Property Owner!  VA Assumable Loan may be possible, don’t miss out!
